title: Cryptocurrency Price Today: Bitcoin Remains Above $30,000 Mark As Compound Becomes Top Gainer - ABP Live
content:
Bitcoin (BTC) and Ethereum (ETH) — two of the most valued crypto coins — managed to rise above the $31,000 and $19,000 marks, respectively, on early Sunday morning. Other popular altcoins — including the likes of Dogecoin (DOGE) and Litecoin (LTC)— landed in the negative as overall prices saw minor losses across the board. Compound (COMP) emerged to be the biggest gainer, seeing a 24-hour jump of over 34.55 percent. Render Token (RNDR), on the other hand, turned out to be the biggest loser.

At the time of writing, the global crypto market cap stood at $1.20 trillion, registering a 24-hour gain of 0.43 percent.

Bitcoin (BTC) price today

Bitcoin price stood at $30,956.90 seeing a 24-hour gain of 0.70 percent, as per CoinMarketCap. According to Indian exchange WazirX, BTC price stood at Rs 26.54 lakhs.

Ethereum (ETH) price today

ETH price stood at $1,913.35, marking a 24-hour gain of 0.96 percent at the time of writing. As per WazirX, Ethereum price in India stood at Rs 1.64 lakhs.

Dogecoin (DOGE) price today

DOGE registered a 24-hour loss of 0.36 percent as per CoinMarketCap data, currently priced at $0.06793. As per WazirX, Dogecoin price in India stood at Rs 5.8001.

Litecoin (LTC) price today

Litecoin saw a 24-hour loss of 2.15 percent. At the time of writing, it was trading at $90.15. LTC price in India stood at Rs 7,820.00.

Ripple (XRP) price today

XRP price stood at $0.491, seeing a 24-hour loss of 0.47 percent. As per WazirX, Ripple price stood at Rs 42.5000.

Solana (SOL) price today

Solana price stood at $17.09, marking a 24-hour loss of 1.66 percent. As per WazirX, SOL price in India stood at Rs 1,470.00.

Top crypto gainers today (June 25)

As per CoinMarketCap data, here are the top five crypto gainers over the past 24 hours:

Compound (COMP)

Price: $41.58

24-hour gain: 34.55 percent

Kava (KAVA)

Price: $1.10

24-hour gain: 14.84 percent

Aave (AAVE)

Price: $66.59

24-hour gain: 14.55 percent

Bitcoin Cash (BCH)

Price: $209.17

24-hour gain: 9.49 percent

Enjin Coin (ENJ)

Price: $0.3152

24-hour gain: 6.24 percent

Top crypto losers today (June 25)

As per CoinMarketCap data, here are the top five crypto losers over the past 24 hours:

Render Token (RNDR)

Price: $2.11

24-hour loss: 3.18 percent

Rocket Pool (RPL)

Price: $39.04

24-hour loss: 2.99 percent

Sui (SUI)

Price: $0.7686

24-hour loss: 2.71 percent

BNB (BNB)

Price: $239.50

24-hour loss: 2.68 percent

eCash (XEC)

Price: $0.00002501
